      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAPIDO KUNA (1) boasts a strong record this course with four wins and two minors from seven tries. Was out of placings last time (30.41) at Cannington in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 11 lengths. Expected to go close. TARAWI (2) is a well performed dog and winner of 14 races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at this track (22.90). Has the ability to give this a shake. RAMBO'S SHOUT (3) hit the ground running last start and was never headed (27.80) at this track in Grade 4/5 over 488m. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. CANYA CELESTE (8) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
